data.description: Voss Farms is a solar powered community for the eco-conscious or sustainable living persons offering energy-efficient housing solutions, for low electric bills.  It also offers  nice amenities including 2 swimming pools, a park, BBQ area, and a covered pavilion. If neighborhood schools and walkability are important to your lifestyle, this home could be an attractive option for you. Come see this delightful cottage-style home offering 1,454 square feet of cozy and inviting living space. The simple open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a spacious and airy feeling.
